      DESC="yp-tools is an implementation of the NIS client tools for Linux
yp-tools is an implementation of the NIS client tools
for Linux and should work with every Linux C Library.
This implementation only provides NIS client tools.
You must already have a ypbind daemon running on the
same host, and a NIS server running somewhere in the net."
